{"tid":1554074,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每個男人，生命中都有兩個好重要嘅女人","createTime":"2019-09-08T23:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T08:34:27.000Z","uid":131245,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9f5e683575be441f2fb770ed7d9a6f6dabfe523a","tid":1554074,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:42:14.000Z","msg":"一個係老母，一個係老婆<br />\n<br />\n啲古惑仔次次出事，會持續不斷去拜山嘅只會係老母，第二就係老婆。<br />\n<br />\n你啲手足幫多你幾次就會話長貧難顧、出面仲有好多兄弟要幫手，請你體諒。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係毒L，又同屋企人嘅關係唔好，咁我祝你好運，你條路會比較難行。"},{"pid":"f5f7a618f0ea0ac8fcde049cf5fa6e83d4c7243c","tid":1554074,"uid":131245,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:43:45.000Z","msg":"我衷心希望你哋口中嘅廢老唔係你哋老豆老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢家真係有少少文革遺風"},{"pid":"0bc4e476dc12634618b3fbe66e6265a1b0465d51","tid":1554074,"uid":267172,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:46:04.000Z","msg":"唔<br />\n我係女人<br />\n我老豆老母都唔撚愛我<br />\n我屌唔屌佢 佢地都唔愛我<br />\n咁我屌得未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n父毒不吃兒呢個痴撚線概念真係害死人"},{"pid":"40485e9163dacb38dad0a8ae821d280634ca6309","tid":1554074,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:46:55.000Z","msg":"古惑仔出事要上庭，通常都捧個老母出嚟話自己好孝順比足家用同法官求情，個老母都要交足戲喊晒口叫法官大人比次機會輕判佢，等佢重新做人、改過自新"},{"pid":"93ab08f29cd375fde760a3f10c7d1c475aa77bf4","tid":1554074,"uid":266336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:48:14.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"f6e3811d6e90296c274d266b0814bddf63e24358","tid":1554074,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:48:24.000Z","msg":"同屋企人因為政見半反面，無老婆，可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d808d1c4076ababc3fd12e8dccafc4112a3a8bfc","tid":1554074,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0bc4e476dc12634618b3fbe66e6265a1b0465d51","tid":1554